¿El mejor matemático? El que tenga el dedo anular mayor
O eso sugiere <a href="http://sciencenow.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/2007/525/1">See Those Fingers? Do the Math</a>.

Visto en <a href="http://science.slashdot.org/article.pl?sid=07/06/02/1339206"> Boys with Longer Ring Fingers are Better at Math</a>.


